*[[File:en/Station list button.png|Lista stacji]] '''[[Main/pl/Lista stacji|Lista stacji/Pl]]:''' Enables you to view a list of stations built by any player.

===Informacje o firmach i przedsiębiorstwach===
*[[File:en/Finances screen button.png|Finances screen]] '''Finances screen button:''' View the finances screen of any company.
*[[File:en/Company information button.png|Company Information]] '''[[Main/en/Transport company|Company]] information button:''' View the company information for any company, and have the possibility to share your competitor's success by buying shares in that company
*[[File:en/Graphs button.png|Graphs]] '''Graphs button:''' View various graphs about companies, their performance and the economy.
